name: MXCPUExceptionDiagnostic
desc: An object representing a diagnostic report for a fatal or nonfatal CPU exception.

items.name: var callStackTree: MXCallStackTree
items.desc: The app call stack associated with the CPU exception.

items.name: var totalCPUTime: Measurement<UnitDuration>
items.desc: The total CPU time used during the exception.

items.name: var totalSampledTime: Measurement<UnitDuration>
items.desc: The total time the app was sampled during the exception.
